Attention all Gamers 🎮 and Audiophiles🎧: 
Ben Baller x Master Dynamic MG20 Premium HD Gaming Headset is dropping November 15 only on the @ntwrk app! @masterdynamic is the Rolls Royce of headphones and personal audio. This collaboration it’s extremely limited, only 200 headsets made and even less available. Get your game on in style! These can also be used as just your everyday high end headphones for personal audio for home or on flights.
NOTE: Compatible with PS4/5, XBOX, PC, Mac and of course all smartphones
